title: Kiss Man Person Dark Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Depicts two men with dark to medium-dark skin tones kissing, representing romantic affection between two males.
apple_vendor_description: This intimate emoji, as rendered on Apple devices, depicts a passionate kiss between two individuals with dark and medium-dark skin tones. A stylized, softly shaded heart hovers between them, glowing with Apple's characteristic realistic lighting and glossy finish, symbolizing deep affection and romance. The faces are rendered with smooth gradients and gentle curves, capturing a moment of tender connection and romantic expression unique to Apple's visual style.
